(14, 'UR18DSL', '9.6-18V Cordless Radio', '9.6 โวลท์-18 โวลท์', '<ol>\r\n	<li>For 9.6V to 18V slide and cassette batteries, backup AA batteries and household power supply</li>\r\n	<li>Can be used to listen to audio equipment like MP3, MD or CD player</li>\r\n	<li>A cell phone is rechargeable with a commercial USB code</li>\r\n	<li>FM/AM digital tuner with LCD display</li>\r\n	<li>FM rod antenna and built-in AM ferrite bar antenna</li>\r\n	<li>76mm dual speakers and bass reflex construction</li>\r\n	<li>Large rotary handle</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Frequency Band: FM</td>\r\n			<td>87.5 to 108MHz</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Frequency Band: AM</td>\r\n			<td>522 to 1,620KHz (Europe)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Antenna: FM</td>\r\n			<td>Rod Antenna</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Antenna: AM</td>\r\n			<td>Ferrite Bar Antenna</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Speaker (diameter)</td>\r\n			<td>76mm (8&Omega;) x 2</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Input Terminal</td>\r\n			<td>AUX IN (&oslash; 3.5mm)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Output Terminal</td>\r\n			<td>Headphone Jack (&oslash; 3.5mm), Charging Jack (5V 0.5A)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Max Available Output</td>\r\n			<td>9.6V: 1.4W x 2, 12V: 2.2W x 2<br />\r\n			14.4V: 3.2W x 2, 18V: 5W x 2</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Power Supply*</td>\r\n			<td>Slide Battery: 14.4V, 18V<br />\r\n			Cassette Battery: 9.6V, 12V, 14.4V, 18V&nbsp;<br />\r\n			Backup Batteries: DC 4.5V, 3 AA Batteries<br />\r\n			Household Power Supply: AC 230V (using provided AC adapter)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Dimensions (L x W x H)</td>\r\n			<td>231 x 184 x 281mm (9-3/32&quot; x 7-1/4&quot; x 11-1/16&quot;)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Weight (without battery)\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>3.3kg (7.3lbs.)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Standard Accessories</td>\r\n			<td>AC Adapter (DC 12V 1A), 3 AA Batteries</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	